items.sentence: Tom was unable to decide who he should vote for.
Tom was up until about 3:00 a.m. reading a book.
Tom was wondering if Mary would go out with him.
Tom asked Mary where he should put his suitcase.
Tom asked me to go to the supermarket with Mary.
Tom bought a book yesterday and gave it to Mary.
Tom came to my office early yesterday afternoon.
I want to go to the store Tom went to yesterday.
I want to have a little chat with you about Tom.
I want to know where I can buy something to eat.
